Packages 
Package Description
org.quifft
Outer package containing QuiFFT object, the primary usage interface of QuiFFT
org.quifft.audioread
Tools for reading waveform data from audio files (supports WAV and MP3)
org.quifft.fft
FFT workhorse, algorithm implemented by Princeton University
org.quifft.output
Output data structures of QuiFFT (classes representing FFT results)
org.quifft.params
Configurable parameters for FFT (window size, normalization, etc)
org.quifft.util
Utility helpers for various classes used by QuiFFT
